01:32:37.200 --> 01:32:49.520
The world doesn't want to say 'Merry Christmas' and now the body of Christ doesn't want to say 'Merry Christmas.

01:32:49.520 --> 01:32:52.400
' Let's give Jesus a day, folks.

01:32:52.400 --> 01:32:54.862
