01:33:57.336 --> 01:34:03.554
I'm saying 'Merry Christmas, Jesus.

01:34:03.554 --> 01:34:07.754
We love you.

01:34:07.754 --> 01:34:09.880
Welcome to our house.

01:34:09.880 --> 01:34:17.640
