01:34:23.413 --> 01:34:26.200
You are welcome in this home.

01:34:26.200 --> 01:34:29.240
' Do you understand?

01:34:29.240 --> 01:34:44.233
When you just get excited about his presence and excited about him coming, he'll come and visit you.

01:34:44.233 --> 01:34:50.904
He comes and visits us.

01:34:50.904 --> 01:34:57.742
