01:36:40.593 --> 01:36:40.947
I plead the blood of Jesus over what I just said.

01:36:50.400 --> 01:36:51.566
And I thank you, God, that your mercy is new every morning and great is his faithfulness.

01:36:51.566 --> 01:36:57.960
