01:36:57.960 --> 01:37:07.960
I'm so glad to get a Holy Ghost spanking because that means he loves me.

01:37:07.960 --> 01:37:12.893
Take me out to the woodshed, Holy Spirit.

01:37:12.893 --> 01:37:26.360
If I'm off on something, when the Holy Spirit takes me out to the woodshed, it means I'm loved.

01:37:51.960 --> 01:37:52.360
Now, Paisley, my little girl, said, 'Did it hurt?

01:37:52.360 --> 01:37:58.650
' when I said I got a spanking today.

01:37:59.760 --> 01:38:00.130
I love her.

01:38:00.130 --> 01:38:16.756
She goes, 'Does it hurt as bad as when you spank me?

01:38:16.756 --> 01:38:19.091
' I said a lot worse.

01:38:19.091 --> 01:38:21.240
She goes, 'Oh, no.

01:38:21.240 --> 01:38:23.599
What does it feel like?

01:38:23.599 --> 01:38:26.606
' I said, 'Well, baby, it's inside.

01:38:26.606 --> 01:38:43.000
' She goes, 'Well, I don't ever know if I want to get a spanking from Jesus.

01:38:43.000 --> 01:38:47.249
' It's funny; her childlike faith is just because she's so real.

01:38:47.249 --> 01:38:48.689
She goes, 'Did it hurt?

01:38:48.689 --> 01:38:51.600
' She cracks me up because she's so real about it.

01:38:51.600 --> 01:38:57.490
She goes, 'What's it feel like when Jesus gives you a spanking?

01:38:57.490 --> 01:39:10.873
Does it hurt like when you spank me?

01:39:10.873 --> 01:40:24.280
' I said, 'Oh, honey, I pray you never do, but I'm sure you will.

01:40:24.280 --> 01:40:35.560
When he corrects you inside, I feel like I'm going to crawl under a rock.

01:40:35.560 --> 01:40:40.840
' And I say, 'Oh, Father, forgive me.

01:40:40.840 --> 01:40:42.400
Help me.

01:40:42.400 --> 01:40:44.960
Make me new.

01:40:44.960 --> 01:40:47.880
Wash me in your blood.

01:40:47.880 --> 01:40:49.800
' "Help me.

01:41:22.217 --> 01:41:25.335
I can't do this on my own without you.

01:41:25.335 --> 01:43:00.600
" And I believe the moment you start doing that and you acknowledge him every day, he'll become so real to you.

01:43:00.600 --> 01:43:11.320
Build a foundation every day by practicing his presence, getting in the Word, and meditating on the Word in prayer.

01:43:11.320 --> 01:43:22.893
"If ye abide in me and my words abide in you, you ask what you will and it shall be done.

01:43:22.893 --> 01:43:34.891
" If you get this book down inside of you, it will change you from the inside out.

01:43:34.891 --> 01:43:47.635
You've got to get this Word of God because it is alive.

01:43:51.737 --> 01:43:52.091
It's him.

01:43:52.091 --> 01:43:54.040
This is God speaking to me.

01:43:54.040 --> 01:44:48.272
This is him speaking to you.

01:44:50.640 --> 01:44:58.000
And you must know this and know your words are powerful.

01:45:05.440 --> 01:45:05.660
Like me, I say things often I shouldn't say.

01:45:05.660 --> 01:45:08.800
He goes, "Brandon, you need to change the way you're talking.

01:45:54.400 --> 01:45:54.711
" So, okay, who wants to pray now?

01:45:54.711 --> 01:45:56.578
I talk too much.

