The Lord brought 64 people in, so they enjoyed it.

01:46:05.895 --> 01:46:09.698
All 64 of you, welcome to the family.

01:46:09.698 --> 01:46:14.040
Father, we thank you for the body.

01:46:14.040 --> 01:46:20.440
We thank you, Lord, tonight for your holy written Word.

01:46:24.476 --> 01:46:31.013
I thank you, Lord, for all that you've said, all that you've done, and all that you continue to do.

01:46:31.013 --> 01:46:33.210
We are wall-to-wall Holy Ghost.

01:46:37.900 --> 01:46:38.320
And as he is, so are we in this world.

01:46:38.320 --> 01:46:45.250
