01:47:20.107 --> 01:47:30.150
No weapon formed against me is going to prosper around my wife, my children, or us.

01:47:38.000 --> 01:47:39.680
And we thank you, Lord, that the angels of the Lord are encamped around about us tonight.

01:47:39.960 --> 01:47:51.394
And I thank you, Lord, that you speak to me uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:47:51.394 --> 01:48:02.360
Father, I thank you now that the blood of Jesus Christ covers me and any visions or anything you show me tonight.

01:48:26.320 --> 01:48:28.028
I thank you, Lord, for the body that was broken for us in Jesus' name, and we're healed and whole by the stripes of Jesus.

01:48:28.028 --> 01:48:31.444
Amen.

01:48:31.444 --> 01:48:34.860
Amen.

01:49:17.240 --> 01:49:30.980
Lord, we take the blood and we make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

01:49:30.980 --> 01:49:41.611
We plead the blood, we apply the blood, and we thank you, Lord, for the blood of Jesus.

