We thank you, Lord, right now we enter into that throne room and we sit at your feet.

01:51:10.830 --> 01:51:24.960
Father, whatever you have us to pray over tonight, if you want to show us something, fine; if not, that's fine, Lord; we just keep coming unto you boldly.

01:51:31.800 --> 01:51:40.280
And we thank you, Father, that you show us that which is to come, and we apply the blood over anything we see so that we're not snared by demonic spirits in Jesus' name.

01:51:40.280 --> 01:51:41.360
Amen and amen.

01:51:41.360 --> 01:51:42.480
Plead the blood.

