You don't want to listen to any familiar spirits.

01:52:57.280 --> 01:53:02.423
They come as an angel of light to try to snare you.

01:53:02.423 --> 01:54:00.817
But I just keep coming underneath the covenant and say, 'God, I know I have a covenant with you, and you're going to keep me from the evil one.

01:54:00.817 --> 01:54:36.240
' He that is born of God, he that is begotten of God keepeth himself, and the wicked one toucheth him not.

