01:56:13.313 --> 01:56:25.791
And he that is begotten, the wicked one touches me not.

01:56:25.791 --> 01:56:31.120
If that's all you've got, that's it.

01:56:31.120 --> 01:56:33.190
Jesus has got me.

01:56:33.190 --> 01:56:41.784
I'm begotten of God and the wicked one toucheth me not.

01:56:41.784 --> 01:56:49.040
Father, I just thank you.

01:56:49.040 --> 01:56:52.400
Oh, Father, we worship you.

01:56:52.400 --> 01:57:05.470
Jesus, we give you praise for your awesomeness.

01:57:05.480 --> 01:57:10.440
Fill our cup, Lord.

01:57:10.440 --> 01:57:15.080
We lift it up, Lord.

01:57:15.080 --> 01:57:18.968
Come and quench this thirsting of our soul.

01:57:18.968 --> 01:57:22.569
Bread of heaven, feed me till I want no more.

01:57:22.569 --> 01:57:30.560
Fill my cup, fill it up, and make me whole.

01:57:30.560 --> 01:57:33.893
I'm seeing something.

