I don't know if that's a good thing.

02:01:54.440 --> 02:01:54.953
You're running out of time.

02:01:54.953 --> 02:01:55.979
Multitudes.

02:01:55.979 --> 02:01:58.820
That's interesting, all that right there.

02:01:58.820 --> 02:02:05.360
All right, the Lord wants to go a different direction now.

02:02:05.360 --> 02:02:15.772
But I can see that water coming inland to that wheat.

02:02:42.315 --> 02:02:43.820
" Okay.

02:02:56.800 --> 02:02:57.600
So say John Kilpatrick was standing right here.

02:03:18.943 --> 02:03:19.217
I see him, but he's skinnier.

02:03:25.840 --> 02:03:35.040
And I see the water come all the way up to his feet and it was divoted out like when you see a wave come in.

