A wave comes in like this, but this came in like a flood.

02:03:39.760 --> 02:03:45.680
It came in like a flood, but it stood right at his feet.

02:03:56.450 --> 02:03:57.920
There was wheat on this side, and the water came right up to his feet.

02:03:59.360 --> 02:04:04.140
